EDF Trading Is Concerned About Distrust in EU Carbon Program

-- B y   M a t h e w   C a r r   a n d   E w a   K r u k o w s k a
-- 
2011-06-02T13:07:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-02/edf-trading-is-concerned-about-distrust-in-eu-carbon-program.html
Instances of fraud in the European
Union’s emissions trading system may lead to “enhanced”
distrust in the cap-and-trade program, Alexander Marty, head of
climate policy at EDF Trading, told a conference in Barcelona.  To contact the reporter on this story:
